title: Rec Hall, west facade. Outside porch/stage added ca. 2003. Flag pole probably of CCC era. Asphalt shingles. Tree groves in background behind building. - Allegheny National Forest, CCC Camp ANF-1 , The camp’s main entrance is located at the intersection of Duhring Road (ANF 131) and ANF 124, Pennsylvania, with the interior site road known as Trail Ride Drive., Marienville, Forest County, PA
